lodash.padstart v4.4.0

The lodash method _.padStart exported as a Node.js module.

Installation

Using npm:

$ {sudo -H} npm i -g npm
$ npm i --save lodash.padstart

In Node.js:

var padStart = require('lodash.padstart');

See the documentation or package source for more details.
